    "text_instructions": [
      {
        "id": "01f0c3a097f0174c950e61d33818635e",
        "content": [
          "Rule type - One specific alerts that has synopsis and Date and CID and all the details like PositionID, Root cause, Case datils and verything in the row.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Most important part is:\r\n",
          "Root Cause - Which alert had what root cause\r\n",
          "Case Details - More detailed description of the root cause\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "You will be asked about new alerts from gold_sql_dp_prod_we_bi_db_dbo_bi_db_compliance_illegal_trades_alerts\r\n",
          "and should analyze them based on historical data rpovided in Regulatory Undertaking Investigations. - This table has Root cause and Case detail which you will have to use and compare CIDs, countries all the data and give conclusion on Possible root cause of the new issue\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Alert specifications:\r\n",
          "PC15 - If position open date is older than 03/03/2024 Root cayse is Legacy\r\n",
          "PC5 / PC36 - If country is Philipines it is most likely System Anomaly like previous cases."
        ]
      }
    ],
    "example_question_sqls": [
      {
        "id": "01f0efb2c80717549456171d4c09f418",
        "question": [
          "For PC13: Check DepositTypeID. Search TranID in Compliance alert type and then use it to search in depsot table by DepositID. TranID=DepositID and then find Deposittypeid and use edictionary to provide what kind of deposit was am"
        ],
        "sql": [
          "WITH pc13_alert AS (\n",
          "  SELECT\n",
          "    `TranID`\n",
          "  FROM\n",
          "    `main`.`bi_db`.`gold_sql_dp_prod_we_bi_db_dbo_bi_db_compliance_illegal_trades_alerts`\n",
          "  WHERE\n",
          "    `AlertType` = 'PC13'\n",
          "    AND YEAR(`Date`) = 2026\n",
          "    AND MONTH(`Date`) = 1\n",
          "    AND `TranID` IS NOT NULL\n",
          "  LIMIT 1\n",
          ")\n",
          "SELECT\n",
          "  d.`DepositID`,\n",
          "  d.`Amount`,\n",
          "  d.`PaymentDate`,\n",
          "  d.`DepositTypeID`,\n",
          "  dict.`DepositType`,\n",
          "  dict.`Description`\n",
          "FROM\n",
          "  pc13_alert a\n",
          "    JOIN `main`.`billing`.`bronze_etoro_billing_deposit` d\n",
          "      ON CAST(a.`TranID` AS INT) = d.`DepositID`\n",
          "    LEFT JOIN `main`.`general`.`bronze_etoro_dictionary_deposittype` dict\n",
          "      ON d.`DepositTypeID` = dict.`DepositTypeID`\n",
          "ORDER BY\n",
          "  d.`PaymentDate` DESC\n",
          "LIMIT 1;"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "01f0fb8adcdd133fa63803b5b6afea38",
        "question": [
          "now calculate the diffrence"
        ],
        "sql": [
          "WITH pc15_alerts AS (\n",
          "  SELECT\n",
          "    `PositionID`\n",
          "  FROM\n",
          "    `main`.`bi_db`.`gold_sql_dp_prod_we_bi_db_dbo_bi_db_compliance_illegal_trades_alerts`\n",
          "  WHERE\n",
          "    `AlertType` = 'PC15'\n",
          "    AND YEAR(`Date`) = 2026\n",
          "    AND MONTH(`Date`) = 1\n",
          "    AND `PositionID` IS NOT NULL\n",
          ")\n",
          "SELECT\n",
          "  p.`PositionID`,\n",
          "  p.`Amount`,\n",
          "  p.`NetProfit`,\n",
          "  (p.`NetProfit` + p.`Amount`) AS total_pnl\n",
          "FROM\n",
          "  pc15_alerts a\n",
          "    JOIN `main`.`dwh`.`dim_position` p\n",
          "      ON a.`PositionID` = p.`PositionID`\n",
          "WHERE\n",
          "  p.`NetProfit` IS NOT NULL\n",
          "ORDER BY\n",
          "  total_pnl ASC;"
        ],
        "usage_guidance": [
          "When we need to know what is the negative amount in PC15 (for potential compensation)"
        ]
      }
